<P1para>
<P2 DocumentURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/uksi/2019/419/regulation/1/1/made" IdURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2019/419/regulation/1/1" id="regulation-1-1">
<Pnumber>1</Pnumber>
<P2para><Text>These Regulations may be cited as the Data Protection, Privacy and Electronic Communications (Amendments etc) (EU Exit) Regulations 2019.</Text>
</P2para>
</P2>
<P2 DocumentURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/uksi/2019/419/regulation/1/2/made" IdURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2019/419/regulation/1/2" id="regulation-1-2">
<Pnumber>2</Pnumber>
<P2para>
<Text>Subject to paragraph (3), they come into force on exit day.</Text>
</P2para>
</P2>
<P2 DocumentURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/uksi/2019/419/regulation/1/3/made" IdURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2019/419/regulation/1/3" id="regulation-1-3">
<Pnumber>3</Pnumber>
<P2para>
<Text>Regulations 7 and 8 and Schedule 4 come into force on 29th March 2019.</Text>
</P2para>
</P2>
<P2 DocumentURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/uksi/2019/419/regulation/1/4/made" IdURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2019/419/regulation/1/4" id="regulation-1-4">
<Pnumber>4</Pnumber>
<P2para>
<Text>An amendment, repeal or revocation made by these Regulations has the same extent in the United Kingdom as the provision to which it relates.</Text>
</P2para>
</P2>
</P1para>
